{
  "script_id": "catenary",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "catenary",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catenary/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "抓住一条项链或电线的两端，让它自然下垂。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catenary",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catenary/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "它会摆出一条优雅的下弯曲线，两端翘起，中间最低。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catenary",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catenary/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26784,
      "text": "这条曲线有个专门的名字，叫做悬链线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catenary",
      "section_id": "cosh",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "cosh-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catenary/cosh-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "悬链线的方程是 y 等于 a 乘以双曲余弦 x 除以 a。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catenary",
      "section_id": "cosh",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "cosh-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catenary/cosh-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "双曲余弦，就是 e 的 x 次方与 e 的负 x 次方之和的一半。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catenary",
      "section_id": "cosh",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "cosh-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catenary/cosh-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.4,
      "size": 38448,
      "text": "参数 a 决定曲线的胖瘦，a 越小垂得越深，a 越大越平坦。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catenary",
      "section_id": "parabola",
      "line_id": "par-1",
      "filename": "parabola-par-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catenary/parabola-par-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.78,
      "size": 28512,
      "text": "很多人以为下垂的链条是抛物线，其实不是。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catenary",
      "section_id": "parabola",
      "line_id": "par-2",
      "filename": "parabola-par-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catenary/parabola-par-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.61,
      "size": 41760,
      "text": "在顶点附近两者几乎重合，但离开中心后，悬链线上升得更快。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catenary",
      "section_id": "parabola",
      "line_id": "par-3",
      "filename": "parabola-par-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catenary/parabola-par-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "伽利略当年也猜成了抛物线，直到后人用微积分才算清真相。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catenary",
      "section_id": "arch",
      "line_id": "arc-1",
      "filename": "arch-arc-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catenary/arch-arc-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.49,
      "size": 23760,
      "text": "把悬链线上下翻转，就得到一道拱。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catenary",
      "section_id": "arch",
      "line_id": "arc-2",
      "filename": "arch-arc-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catenary/arch-arc-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "这样的拱只承受压力，没有弯矩，是最省力的形状。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catenary",
      "section_id": "arch",
      "line_id": "arc-3",
      "filename": "arch-arc-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catenary/arch-arc-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "高迪设计圣家堂时，就用倒挂的链条模型来寻找这种拱。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catenary",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catenary/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "调整参数 a，看曲线在深与平之间连续变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catenary",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catenary/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "打开对比抛物线，再点倒置，亲眼看看它变成拱的样子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catenary",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catenary/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "悬链线是柔软链条自然下垂的形状，方程用双曲余弦描述。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catenary",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catenary/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "它像抛物线却不是，倒过来又成为最优的受压拱。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "catenary",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/catenary/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "一条链条里藏着这么多数学，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 34.21,
  "total_size": 547200,
